聲明<br />\n<a href=\"https://martinoei.com/article/28993/hong-kong-act-1985-%e8%88%87%e8%81%af%e5%90%88%e8%81%b2%e6%98%8e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmartinoei.com%2Farticle%2F28993%2Fhong-kong-act-1985-%25e8%2588%2587%25e8%2581%25af%25e5%2590%2588%25e8%2581%25b2%25e6%2598%258e&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmoGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=9d6c613f\" target=\"_blank\">https://martinoei.com/article/28993/hong-kong-act-1985-%e8%88%87%e8%81%af%e5%90%88%e8%81%b2%e6%98%8e</a>"},{"pid":"fc48222b6cfd7dfd2c548c120b9ba3adae616192","tid":2100352,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T03:21:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來你係獨立黨班共匪既手下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即係共匪啦，廢事同你講咁多<br />\n中共一直話中英聯合聲明係歷史文件、已經無效，你仆到去幫佢叫無效，你仲唔係自認共匪係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃世澤篇文解釋好清楚點解唔廢得聯合聲明<br />\nHong Kong Act 1985 與聯合聲明<br />\n<a href=\"https://martinoei.com/article/28993/hong-kong-act-1985-%e8%88%87%e8%81%af%e5%90%88%e8%81%b2%e6%98%8e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmartinoei.com%2Farticle%2F28993%2Fhong-kong-act-1985-%25e8%2588%2587%25e8%2581%25af%25e5%2590%2588%25e8%2581%25b2%25e6%2598%258e&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmoGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=9d6c613f\" target=\"_blank\">https://martinoei.com/article/28993/hong-kong-act-1985-%e8%88%87%e8%81%af%e5%90%88%e8%81%b2%e6%98%8e</a></blockquote><br />\n雜總呼吸　你呼吸仲唔係佢特派間碟？<br />\n黃世澤推理滑坡　泛民捉鬼　獨立黨鬧晒屈晒其他所有人<br />\n香港政圈社運圈老一輩就係咁o既混水<br />\n而你根本連閱讀理解都有問題"}]}